snippet.title: Ash of Gods: The Way | Story Trailer & Prologue Release
snippet.description:
You’re sent right into the enemy’s territory on a mission to save your country. Will you come back alive, or end up on the gallows?

Ash of Gods: The Way is releasing on April 27th, 2023.

As of April 17th 2023, the Ash of Gods: The Way Prologue is no longer available.

Wishlist Ash of Gods: The Way on Steam: http://bit.ly/3l0RFQg

For more information check out our pages: 

* Website: https://bit.ly/3P8uX3i 
* Steam store: http://bit.ly/3l0RFQg
* Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/Ash_of_Gods/ 
* Twitter: https://twitter.com/ashofgods 

Or join us on Discord: https://discord.gg/ashofgods
